https://i.imgur.com/3L1NeYF.png

Agricultural products branch. 
Crop formulas are obtained through Farmer NPC quests, crafted items formulas are obtained through Science NPC quests.

https://i.imgur.com/wGC6ohD.png

Alloys branch.
Recipes can be randomly acquired in Manufacturing Plants and Operations Centers.

https://i.imgur.com/If51Mnj.png

Gas products branch. 
Raw gases obtained by building atmosphere harvesters on adequate planets (requires materials from the Agricultural branch), buying them from traders (not trade terminals) or as secondary resources.
Enhanced Gas recipes can be obtained in Manufacturing Plants.  Manufactured Gas Product recipes can be obtained in Operations Centers.
Underligned items can be acquired as mission rewards.
